These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-1::.
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, horse, ferret, goldfish
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, amaryllis, bellflower, lily
1. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rabbit##5
2. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the person who growszinnia##3
3. the person who growszinnia is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the person who growslily##5
5. the person who growszinnia is the owner of the horse##1
6. the owner of the ferret is the person who growsamaryllis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Pet      | goldfish  | rabbit | horse  | ferret |
| Flower   | bellflower | lily      | zinnia | amaryllis |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, rock-climbing, traveling, card-games
4 different games are played: monopoly, bridge, chess, canasta
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person playing monopoly and the person playing canasta##2
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the left of the person playing canasta##5
3. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing chess##1
4. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
5. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby   | card-games | traveling | rock-climbing   | woodworking |
| Game           | chess      | monopoly    | bridge | canasta      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, juice, milk, 7up
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, may, july, august
1. the person drinking juice is the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##5
4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
5. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in august##5
6. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |     3     |   4    |
| Beverage        | juice | tea | milk     | 7up |
| Birthday   | may  | august   | july | april    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, aquamarine, brown, lilac
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, indie, classical, hip-hop
1. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
2. the person who likes lilac is somewhere to the right of the fan of classical##5
3. the person who likes apricot is between the fan of hip-hop and the fan of indie##2
4. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
5. the fan of hip-hop is the person who likes brown##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Color         | brown | apricot | aquamarine | lilac |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop   | classical     | indie    | reggae       |

