.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-5::.
4 different pets are kept: frog, guinea-pig, bird, snake
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, golf, tennis, sailing
1. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5
2. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
3. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the left of the owner of the frog##5
4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
6. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3     |    4    |
| Pet          | bird | snake   | frog   | guinea-pig    |
| Sport   | golf  | sailing | cricket | tennis |

