.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-6::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, sailing, handball, soccer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, family, animation, musical
1. the person who's sport is soccer is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is somewhere to the left of the person watching musical movies##5
3. the person watching musical movies is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person watching animation movies##2
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |       3        |     4     |
| Sport           | skateboarding | sailing | soccer | handball |
| Movie-Genre   | animation        | musical     | martial-arts       | family   |

