.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-7::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, security-guard, freelancer, teacher
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, dunhill, ritmeester, tiparillo
1. the dunhill-smoker is the teacher##1
2. the coach is between the security-guard and the ritmeester-smoker##2
3. the bongani-smoker is in an even position##4
4. the tiparillo-smoker is somewhere to the left of the coach##5
5. the coach is in an even position##4
6. the freelancer is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Job   | security-guard | coach  | freelancer  | teacher   |
| Cigar           | tiparillo  | bongani | ritmeester | dunhill |

