2. the person who growsdaisy is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is golf##5
3. the person who growsdaisy is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
4. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is baseball##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Flower   | iris     | daisy | tulip     | bellflower   |
| Sport    | badminton | cricket  | golf | baseball |

