1. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
5. the person watching satire movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching family movies##5
6. the person watching family movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching epic movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |  4   |
