.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, dubstep, techno, pop
There 4 different types of food: spinach, lime, strawberry, grapes
1. the fan of techno is on the left or right of the person eating lime##3
2. the person eating spinach is somewhere to the left of the fan of pop##5
3. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the right of the fan of dubstep##5
4. the person eating spinach is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapes##5
5. the person eating lime is somewhere to the left of the fan of house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | techno       | house   | pop        |
| Food      | lime  | grapes | spinach | strawberry |

