.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-11::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, chestnut, amber, turquise
There 4 different types of food: zucchini, cabbage, plum, cucumber
1. the person who likes purple is somewhere to the left of the person who likes chestnut##5
2. the person eating plum is the person who likes amber##1
3. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
4. the person who likes turquise is somewhere to the right of the person eating plum##5
5. the person eating cabbage is somewhere to the left of the person eating zucchini##5
6. the person eating zucchini is on the left or right of the person eating cabbage##3
7. the person who likes amber is somewhere to the right of the person eating zucchini##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4      |
| Color   | purple | chestnut   | amber | turquise     |
| Food   | cabbage     | zucchini | plum  | cucumber |

