2. the owner of the hedgehog is in an even position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5
4. the person who's birthday is in june is the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in november##5
6. the owner of the dog is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |  4   |
| Birthday   | june | november        | january        | may |
| Pet         | goldfish  | hedgehog | rat | dog |

