.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-14::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, analyst, firefighter, lawyer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, r&b, techno, metal
1. the police-officer is somewhere to the right of the fan of techno##5
2. the firefighter is somewhere to the right of the fan of punk##5
3. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of metal##1
4. the fan of metal is the firefighter##1
5. the analyst is somewhere to the right of the police-officer##5
6. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |    4     |
| Job   | lawyer  | police-officer | analyst | firefighter |
| Music-Genre   | techno | punk | r&b   | metal  |

