3. the cape-cod house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
4. the townhouse house is somewhere to the right of the person watching time-travel movies##5
5. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching documentary movies##5
6. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |      3       |     4     |
| House   | art-deco | townhouse  | farmhouse      | cape-cod |
| Movie-Genre     | time-travel    | documentary | adventure | spy   |

