2. the person traveling to new-york is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the owner of the rabbit is in an even position##4
5. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to new-york##5
6. the person traveling to marseilles is between the person traveling to hannover and the owner of the goat##2
7. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to hannover##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| City      | hannover   | marseilles  | nizza      | new-york       |
| Pet   | hamster | mouse | goat | rabbit |

