3. the art-deco house is on the right of the tower house##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
5. the victorian house is on the right of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk     | juice | lemonade | iced-tea |
| House     | tower | art-deco    | victorian    | modern |

