.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-18::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, gardening, rock-climbing, singing
4 different pets are kept: ferret, frog, chinchilla, rat
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rat##5
3. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
4. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
5. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is between the person who's hobby is singing and the owner of the frog##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |       4       |
| Hobby      | rock-climbing     | singing | hiking     | gardening |
| Pet   | chinchilla | rat  | ferret | frog        |

