.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-19::.
4 different games are played: whist, canasta, chess, poker
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, bongani, bolivar, pall-mall
1. the person playing whist is between the bongani-smoker and the person playing canasta##2
2. the fonseca-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person playing poker##5
3. the person playing chess is somewhere to the left of the pall-mall-smoker##5
4. the bongani-smoker is on the left or right of the fonseca-smoker##3
5. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Game         | chess   | poker   | whist       | canasta   |
| Cigar   | bolivar | bongani | fonseca | pall-mall |

