.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, lavender, ebony, emerald
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, camping, gardening, collecting
1. the person who likes lavender is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is camping##5
2. the person who likes orange is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##5
5. the person who likes lavender is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##5
6. the person who likes orange is between the person who likes emerald and the person who's hobby is photography##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Color        | lavender     | emerald | orange | ebony |
| Hobby   | gardening | collecting | camping      | photography        |

 